%20%26quot%3Bmisfortune%20of%20democracy%26quot%3B.%20According%20to%20her%20affidavit%2C%20Ms%20Thakur%20has%20studied%20till%20class%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20misfortune%20of%20democracy%20that%20people%20who%20hold%20constitutional%20posts%20and%20are%20responsible%20for%20big%20departments%20are%20not%20competent%20even%20in%20their%20mother%20tongue.%20How%20can%20they%20be%20capable%20of%20running%20their%20ministry%3F%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0Mr%20Mishra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra%20further%20suggested%20amending%20the%20Constitution%20to%20establish%20minimum%20educational%20qualifications%20for%20election%20candidates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20country's%20citizens%20are%20being%20claimed%20to%20be%20literate%2C%20while%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there%20is%20lack%20of%20literacy%20among%20the%20responsible%20people.%20So%20what%20is%20the%20truth%3F%20This%20is%20an%20issue%20related%20to%20the%20system%20and%20not%20to%20any%20individual%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202015%2C%20the%20'Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao'%20is%20a%20central%20government%20scheme%20to%20address%20declining%20child%20sex%20ratio%20and%20women's%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhar%20district%20BJP%20president%20Manoj%20Somani%20defended%20Ms%20Thakur%2C%20accusing%20the%20Congress%20of%20harbouring%20%26quot%3Bpetty%20and%20anti-tribal%20thinking.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSavitri%20ji's%20feelings%20and%20sentiments%20are%20pure%2C%20but%20Congressmen%20are%20not%20able%20to%20keep%20their%20sentiments%20pure.%20The%20tribal%20community%20will%20not%20forgive%20the%20insult%20of%20a%20tribal%20woman%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20Umang%20Singhar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20tribal%20leader%20from%20Dhar%2C%20echoed%20the%20criticism%20on%20social%20media.%20Mr%20Singhar%20