0Over%209%20lakh%20candidates%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20which%20is%20held%20for%20Assistant%20Professor%20posts%20in%20universities%20and%20colleges%20and%20to%20determine%20eligibility%20for%20junior%20research%20fellowships.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20triggered%20an%20immediate%20reaction%20from%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20who%20called%20out%20the%20government%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Blaxity%26quot%3B%20and%20demanded%20that%20accountability%20be%20fixed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20said%20the%20June%20exam%20of%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission-National%20Eligibility%20Test%20(UGC-NET)%20was%20conducted%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20OMR%20(pen%20and%20paper)%20mode%20in%20two%20shifts%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%2019th%20June%2C%202024%2C%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20received%20certain%20inputs%20from%20National%20Cyber%20Crime%20Threat%20Analytics%20Unit%20of%20Indian%20Cyber%20Crime%20Coordination%20Centre%20(I4C)%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20on%20the%20Examination.%20These%20inputs%20prima%20facie%20indicate%20that%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20aforesaid%20examination%20may%20have%20been%20compromised%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20said%20it%20was%20announcing%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20June%202024%20examination%20%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20transparency%20and%20sanctity%20of%20the%20examination%20process%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20will%20be%20held%20afresh%20at%20a%20date%20which%20will%20be%20shared%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20reports%20of%20the%20paper%20of%20the%20examination%20being%20leaked%2C%20but%20this%20was%20not%20confirmed%20by%20the%20ministry.%20It%20said%20only%20that%20the%20matter%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20for%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UGC-NET%20is%20conducted%20twice%20every%20year%2C%20in%20June%20and%20December.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20UGC%20Chairman%20M%20Jagadesh%20Kumar%20had%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20NTA%20has%20successfully%20conducted%20UGC%20-%20NET%20June%202024%20for%20determining%20the%20eligible%20candidates%20for%20(i)%20'award%20of%20Junior%20Research%20Fellowship%20and%20appointment%20as%20Assistant%20Professor'%2C%20(ii)%20'appointment%20as%20Assistant%20Professor%20and%20admission%20to%20Ph.D.'%20and%20(iii)%20'admission%20to%20Ph.D.%20only'%20in%2083%20subjects%20in%20OMR%20(Pen%20and%20Paper)%20mode%20in%20two%20(02)%20different%20shifts%20(09%3A30%20AM%20to%2012%3A30%20Noon%20and%2003%3A00%20PM%20to%2006%3A00%20PM).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20examination%20has%20been%20conducted%20at%201%2C205%20Exam%20Centres%20in%20317%20cities%20across%20the%20country%20for%2011%2C21%2C225%20candidates.%20Out%20of%20the%20total%20registered%20candidates%2C%20about%2081%25%20candidates%20appeared%20for%20the%20exam.%20Best%20wishes%20to%20all%20the%20candidates%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20written.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENEET%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2024%20lakh%20students%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses%2C%20which%20is%20also%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20on%20May%205.%20The%20results%20were%20announced%20on%20June%204%2C%2010%20days%20before%20schedule%2C%20but%20allegations%20of%20a%20question%20paper%20leak%20and%20grace%20marks%20to%20over%201%2C500%20students%20triggered%20protests.%20Cases%20were%20also%20filed%20in%20courts%2C%20including%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20NTA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20NEET%2C%20the%20ministry's%20statement%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20related%20to%20grace%20marks%20has%20already%