E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20could%20drop%20a%20pacer%20and%20include%20Kuldeep%20in%20the%20team%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20tough%20was%20it%20to%20leave%20Kuldeep%2C%20who%20has%20been%20India's%20standout%20spinner%20over%20the%20past%2012%20months%2C%20out%20of%20playing%20eleven%20in%20USA%3F%20%E2%80%9CIt's%20tough%20to%20leave%20anyone%20out.%20I%20mean%20all%20the%20four%20guys%20that%20we%20left%20out%20in%20those%20games%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20are%20all%20quality%20players.%20It's%20just%20that%20the%20conditions%20and%20what%20we%20felt%20was%20the%20requirement%20in%20that%20particular%20venue%20made%20us%20go%20with%20that%20particular%20combination%20where%20we%20felt%20that%20there%20wasn't%20a%20huge%20role%20for%20spin%20and%20it%20was%20more%20of%20pace%20more%20of%20kind%20of%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20also%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20had%20the%20depth%20on%20those%20tricky%20kind%20of%20tickets%20.%20So%20that's%20what%20we%20went%20there%20with.%20You%20know%2C%20it%20might%20be%20different%20here.%20Without%20giving%20too%20much%20away%2C%20certainly.%20You%20know%2C%20it%20might%20be%20slightly%20different%20here.%20That%20you%20might%20need%20an%20extra%20spinner%20and%20then%20someone%20like%20Kuldeep%20or%20Yuzi%20can%20come%20into%20play.%20They%20become%20a%20very%20good%20factor%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dravid%20ahead%20of%20the%20Afghanistan%20fixture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20have%20definitely%20pushed%20the%20needle%20in%20batting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20were%20guilty%20of%20being%20too%20conservative%20in%20their%20approach%20in%20the%20previous%20two%20editions%20of%20T20%20World%20Cup%20but%20Dravid%20feels%20the%20team%20has%20turned%20the%20tide%20on%20that%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20actually%20been%20to%20be%20able%20to%20push%20the%20needle%20forward%20in%20terms%20of%20our%20batting%20there.%20Sometimes%20in%20