nemic.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echilling%20effects%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20investing%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVenture%20capital%20has%20cyclical%20fluctuations%2C%20but%20Scott%20Stanford%2C%20a%20cofounder%20and%20partner%20at%20ACME%20Capital%2C%20an%20early-stage%20VC%20firm%2C%20thinks%20something%20more%20meaningful%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20crazy%20to%20think%20half%20the%20VC%20firms%20that%20were%20actively%20investing%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20will%20be%20sidelined%20and%20eventually%20collapse%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20wave%20will%20die%20off%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20Ten%20years%20from%20now%2C%20the%20damage%20will%20be%20evident%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20simple%20back-of-the-napkin%20math%20paints%20a%20grim%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20chart%20compiled%20by%20Stanford%20and%20shared%20with%20BI%2C%20by%201990%2C%20there%20were%20300%20VC%20firms%20overseeing%20%2417%20billion%20in%20assets.%20Over%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20those%20numbers%20went%20through%20the%20roof.%20Now%2C%20there%20are%203%2C000%20VC%20firms%20overseeing%20%241.2%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20exits%20is%20modest%20at%20best.%20By%201990%2C%20VC-backed%20IPOs%20totaled%20%2412.7%20billion.%20By%202021%2C%20that%20increased%20to%20%2460.1%20billion.%20And%20it's%20a%20similar%20story%20with%20VC-backed%20M%26amp%3BA%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20venture%20industry%20got%20ahead%20of%20itself%2C%20in%20other%20words%3A%20The%20proliferation%20of%20firms%20and%20the%20money%20they're%20managing%20is%20not%20supported%20by%20the%20financial%20value%20they're%20creating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20venture%20capital%20industry%20matured%20over%20the%20past%20several%20decades%2C%20euphoric%20momentum%20investors%2C%20not%20technologists%2C%20drove%20the%20creation%20of%20funds%20and%20the%20deployment%20of%20capital%2C%20blind%20to%20the%20nuances%20and%20challenges%20of%20timing%20innovation%20cycles%2C%26quot%3B%20Stanford%20and%20ACME%20cofounder%20Hany%20Nada%20told%20investors%20in%20a%20recent%20letter%20shared%20with%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20as%20investors%20mistime%20specific%20investments%20or%20funds%2C%20the%20venture%20industry%20as%20a%20whole%20got%20as%20much%20as%20a%20decade%20or%20two%20ahead%20of%20reality%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20overcrowded%2C%20overcapitalized%2C%20and%20overvalued%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2203af2507-6311-43f3-ae85-0c2bb24e15b1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVC%20backers%20have%20other%20options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20factors%20will%20serve%20to%20cull%20the%20herd%20in%20VC%2C%20per%20Stanford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELimited%20partners%20(LPs)%2C%20or%20investors%20who%20put%20money%20into%20venture%20firms%2C%20have%20other%20options%20thanks%20to%20higher%20interest%20rates%2C%20Stanford%20added.%20Low-risk%20investments%20like%20investing%20in%20Treasury%20bonds%2C%20for%20one%20example%2C%20are%20commanding%20a%20decent%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20longer%20an%20elusive%20sprite%20commanding%20irrational%20M%26amp%3BA%20premiums%20or%20IPO%20exuberance%2C%26quot%3B%20Stanford%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20a%20startup%20claiming%20they%20were%20a%20tech%20company%20somewhere%20in%20their%20pitch%20deck%20might%20command%20a%20billion-dollar%20valuation.%20That%20era%20is%20long%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20AI%20isn't%20necessarily%20the%20next%20panacea%2C%20Stanford%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20is%20out%20on%20whether%20it%20spawns%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20unicorns%20%E2%80%94%20when%20leaders%20like%20OpenAI%20are%20providing%20the%20tech%20openly%2C%20and%20anyone%20can%20use%20it%20to%20spin%20up%20decent%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20told%2C%20in%20this%20environment%2C%20investors%20without%20deep%20expertise%2C%20powerful%20networks%2C%20or%20mega-funds%20to%20deploy%20will%20be%20hard-pressed%20to%20raise%20money%20and%20build%20enduring%20franchises%2C%20Stanford%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20VC%20without%20capital%20is%20like%20a%20tennis%20player%20without%20a%20racquet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20give%20interviews%20and%20make%20headlines%20but%20they%20aren't%20invited%20on%20the%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ACME%20Capital%20team.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667350e4087acd2be9b4edd3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20ACME%20Capital%20team.%3Cp%3EACME%20Capital%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273f0b2e9-ab0b-4b58-a988-7c2cd0c879b8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVCs%20will%20have%20to%20take%20risks%20again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStanford%20believes%20today's%20challenges%20will%20give%20way%20to%20a%20new%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20rather%2C%20an%20old%20%E2%80%94%20era%20of%20VC%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETons%20of%20startups%20that%20went%20to%20market%20in%20the%20last%20handful%20of%20years%20had%20a%20similar%20strategy%3A%20Backed%20with%20millions%20in%20funding%2C%20they%20launched%20an%20app%20that%20was%20slightly%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebetter%20than%20someone%20else's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20you%20could%20get%20away%20with%20making%20social%20features%2C%20apps%2C%20and%20incrementally%20better%20software%20in%20this%20fashion%2C%20Stanford%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENowadays%2C%20incumbents%20can%20do%20all%20that%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20investors%20that%20survive%20the%20contraction%20will%20have%20to%20back%20companies%20that%20are%20actually%20inventing%20things%20and%20therefore%20come%20with%20a%20sizable%20risk%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20tho