ndustry%20profoundly.%20But%3Cspan%3E%2C%20according%20to%20a%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.citi.com%2Fgps%2F9j79xHIa-vfPi785TYiSciffO0j4I0D52fI9LrahsLZEo6MpT4aM7SpwSFagAL9CIukqn2fwiJ_GNvDsLy4b6XEjftdK1abu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enew%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0from%20Citigroup%20researchers%2C%20%26quot%3Bfinance%20will%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20changes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20bank%20or%20financial%20firm%20looks%20like%20in%20the%20mid-2020s%2C%20be%20it%20retail%20or%20wholesale%20finance%2C%20looks%20very%20different%20to%20the%20mid-1980s%2C%20or%20the%20mid-1940s%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%20%26quot%3BAI%20will%20repeat%20this%20cycle%2C%20possibly%20speeding%20it%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20general-purpose%20technologies%2C%20or%20GPTs%2C%20create%20new%20opportunities%20for%20innovation%20and%20can%20improve%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20also%20destroy%20existing%20ways%20of%20doing%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20as%20such%2C%20they%20also%20create%20losers%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20short%20term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20data%20pulled%20from%20Accenture%20Research%20and%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%2C%20Citi's%20researchers%20said%20that%20about%2067%25%20of%20banking%20jobs%20have%20%26quot%3Bhigher%20potential%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20automated%20or%20augmented%20by%20AI.%20That%20means%20%26quot%3Bbanking%20jobs%26quot%3B%20(which%20the%20report%20didn't%20narrowly%20define)%20have%20the%20highest%20potential%20for%20AI-led%20job%20displacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20Citi%2C%20a%20decline%20in%20head%20count%20may%20be%20partially%20or%20completely%20offset%20by%20an%20increase%20in%20AI-related%20compliance%20managers%20and%20ethics%20and%20governance%20staff.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20upside%20Citi%20pointed%20out%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20they%20estimate%20the%20profit%20pool%20for%20the%202023%20global%20banking%20sector%20%26quot%3Bcould%20increase%209%25%20or%20%24170%20billion%20from%20the%20adoption%20of%20AI%2C%20rising%20from%20just%20over%20%241.7%20trillion%20to%20close%20to%20%242%20trillion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22809%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Citi%20chart%20on%20AI's%20impact%20on%20finance%20jobs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66733358a76074d191cd3e54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22404%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPart%20of%20page%2022%20of%20Citi's%20report.%3Cp%3ECiti's%20AI%20in%20FInance%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255206a59-8c97-4ea0-9092-6016a29b5a8f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20adoption%20in%20finance%20will%20be%20slow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Citi%20researchers%20believe%20the%20%26quot%3Bpace%20of%20implementing%20modern%20AI%20tools%20in%20financial%20services%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20GenAI%2C%20will%20be%20relatively%20slow%20when%20compared%20to%20other%20sectors%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20the%20report%2C%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20regulated%20nature%20of%20the%20sector%20and%20lack%20of%20'ready%20to%20go%20globally%20aligned%20rules.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20regulatory%20landscape%20is%20evolving%20in%20some%20jurisdictions%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20challenging%20road%20ahead%20for%20financial%20services%20firms%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20implementation%20because%20countries%20are%20moving%20to%20different%20speeds%2C%20taking%20different%20approaches%20towards%20regulation%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20changing%20their%20position%20on%20whether%20to%20regulate%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20featured%20in%20the%20report%2C%20Shameek%20Kundu%2C%20the%20head%20of%20financial%20services%20and%20chief%20strategy%20officer%20at%20TruEra%2C%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20same%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20describe%20traditional%20AI%20adoption%20in%20financial%20services%20as%3A%20widespread%2C%20shallow%2C%20and%20inconsequential%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kundu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKundu%20explains%20that%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Ba%20large%20number%20of%20enterprises%20experimenting%20with%20AI%20across%20different%20use%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20yet%20%26quot%3Blimited%20scale%20of%20AI%20adoption%20across%20use%20cases%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Blimited%20perceived%20impact%20of%20AI%20system%20failures%20on%20critical%20business%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20a%202022%20Bank%20of%20England%20survey%2C%20which%20found%20that%20%26quot%3B72%25%20of%20firms%20reported%20using%20or%20developing%20machine%20learning%20applications%2C%26quot%3B%20yet%20the%20%26quot%3Bmedian%20number%20of%20ML%20applications%20for%20mainstream%20UK%20financial%20institutions%20to%20be%20just%2020-30%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bless%20than%2020%25%20of%20the%20already%20few%20AI%20use%20cases%20were%20critical%20to%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-could-automate-more-than-half-of-banking-jobs-citi-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718828116000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667337392efa138e0330ffa3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-could-automate-more-than-half-of-banking-jobs-citi-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20Citi%20report%20says%20finance%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20forefront%26quot%3B%20of%20changes%20due%20to%20artificial%20intelligence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ebrownstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Emmalyse%20Brownstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A112%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-could-automate-more-than-ha