including%2C%20without%20limitation%2C%20seizure%20and%20injunction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20asked%20the%20company%20to%20provide%20written%20documentation%20of%20the%20steps%20it%20is%20taking%20to%20prevent%20future%20violations%20within%2015%20business%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Dollar%20Tree%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20retailer%20is%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bjourney%20to%20transform%20our%20business%26quot%3B%20under%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-tree-shoppers-angry-dollar-store-raises-prices-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20management%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20will%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20significantly%20enhance%20and%20strengthen%20our%20compliance%20and%20safety%20programs%20and%20capabilities%2C%20including%20our%20process%20for%20quickly%20and%20effectively%20executing%20product%20recalls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20cooperate%20with%20FDA%20on%20this%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-dollar-close-stores-relocate-rebrand-others-dollar-tree-ceo-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Dollar%20Tree's%20leadership%20team%20in%20the%20last%2018%20months.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.dollartree.com%2Fnews-media%2Fpress-releases%2Fdetail%2F238%2Frick-dreiling-to-assume-role-of-chairman-and-chief%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERick%20Dreiling%20replaced%20Mike%20Witynski%20as%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%202023%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.dollartree.com%2Fnews-media%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F9698%2Fnew-leadership-appointments-in-dollar-tree-family-dollar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJason%20Nordin%20joined%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20senior%20vice%20president%20and%20chief%20of%20stores%20for%20Dollar%20Tree%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the