allenge%20PM%20Modi%20to%20start%20preparations%20today%20-%20keeping%20this%20fake%20Shiv%20Sena%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20also%20rubbished%20speculation%20about%20the%20two%20Sena%20factions%20joining%20hands%20and%20remaining%20in%20the%20NDA%20fold.%20He%20would%20never%20go%20with%20those%20who%20tried%20to%20%26quot%3Bfinish%20off%26quot%3B%20his%20party%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20rebel%20faction%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde%20was%20awarded%20the%20name%20and%20election%20symbol%20of%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20the%20voters%20had%20decisively%20settled%20the%20legacy%20issue.%20And%20they%20did%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20poll%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20won%20nine%20seats%20and%20the%20Shinde%20faction%20seven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20party%20in%20the%20same%20boat%2C%C2%A0%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20won%20eight%20seats.%20The%20faction%20led%20by%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%20--%20which%20also%20got%20the%20name%20and%20party%20symbol%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20--%20only%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlly%20Congress%20won%2013%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people's%20disapproval%20of%20the%20political%20upheaval%20in%20the%20state%20extended%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20once%20let%20slip%2C%20had%20engineered%20the%20Sena%20split.%20The%20party's%20score%20was%20cut%20down%20to%20nine%20seats%2C%20from%2023%20in%202019%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20remained%20determined%20to%20push%20the%20point%20he%20based%20his%20rebellion%20on%20--%20that%20Mr%20Thackeray%20had%20strayed%20from%20the%20ideology%20set%20down%20by%20Sena%20founder%20and%20his%20father%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20has%20your%20Hindutva%20gone%3F%20You%20have%20no%20right%20to%20seek%20votes%20in%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray's%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20massive%20rally%20in%20Worli's%20NSCI%20dome.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BEven%20a%20small%20kid%20will%20tell%20you%20that%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%20won%20because%20of%20the%20Congress'%20vote%20bank.%20Those%20who%20left%20Bal%20Thackeray's%20thoughts%20for%20position%2C%20lost%20in%20the%20election.%20Bal%20Thackeray%20always%20talked%20against%20the%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Mr%20Thackeray%20had%20already%20covered%20the%20point.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20got%20votes%20of%20all%20patriots%2C%20people%20of%20all%20religions.%20They%20said%20we%20left%20Hindutva%2C%20because%20we%20went%20with%20the%20Congress.%20I%20did%20not%20leave%20Hindutva.%20If%20everyone%20voted%20for%20us%20to%20save%20the%20country%20and%20the%20constitution%2C%20then%20people%20are%20with%20us.%20It%20shows%20the%20BJP%20is%20the%20one%20that%20left%20Hindutva%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718822340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fmg6p0jn_uddhav-thackeray-1200_625x300_20_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsena-vs-sena-you-vs-me-in-maharashtra-uddhav-thackerays-challenge-for-pm-narendra-modi-5925752%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sena%20Versus%20Sena%20battle%20heated%20up%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20foundation%20day%20as%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Eknath%20Shinde%20held%20parallel%20programmes%20in%20two%20parts%20of%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsena-vs-sena-you-vs-me-in-maharashtra-uddhav-thackerays-challenge-for-pm-narendra-modi-5925752%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsena-vs-sena-you-vs-me-in-maharashtra-u