E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CNBC%2C%20Maman%20made%20about%20%2447.2%20million%20in%20sales%20last%20year%20and%20hopes%20to%20bring%20in%20%2465%20million%20in%20total%20revenue%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20an%20easy%20start%20%E2%80%94%20from%20draining%20their%20savings%20to%20expanding%20the%20brand%2C%20co-founders%20Marshall%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Benjamin%20Sormonte%2C%20gave%20up%20a%20lot%20to%20get%20the%20business%20where%20it%20is%20today.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC%20Make%20It%2C%20they%20described%20how%20they%20spent%20the%20last%20decade%20making%20their%20Parisian%20fantasy%20into%20a%20lucrative%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287433d72-1055-4f53-adeb-c48620ae0731%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20sacrifices%20at%20the%20onset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20many%20small%20businesses%2C%20starting%20up%20was%20not%20easy.%20Marshall%20and%20Sormonte%20gave%20up%20a%20lot%20%E2%80%94%20including%20money%2C%20jobs%2C%20and%20sleep%20%E2%80%94%20to%20pursue%20their%20dream%20of%20running%20a%20successful%20caf%C3%A9%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20opening%2C%20they%20took%20their%20first%20leap%20of%20faith%20by%20uprooting%20their%20lives%20to%20relocate.%20Marshall%20and%20Sormonte%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20in%202012%20from%20Spain%20after%20running%20a%20beach%20club%20in%20Ibiza.%20Before%20that%2C%20they%20had%20corporate%20jobs%20in%20law%20and%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20time%20to%20bring%20the%20cafe%20to%20life%20physically%2C%20Sormonte%20and%20Marshall%20became%20not%20only%20business%20owners%20but%20also%20painters%2C%20bakers%2C%20and%20waiters.%20When%20Maman%20opened%20its%20doors%20in%20October%202014%2C%20they%20spent%20upwards%20of%2080%20hours%20a%20week%20working%20at%20the%20downtown%20Manhattan%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20sacrifice%2C%26quot%3B%20Sormonte%20told%20CNBC%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20sweat%20and%20tears%20and%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20burned%20about%20%24250%2C000%20to%20open%2C%20including%20emptying%20their%20savings%20accounts%20and%20turning%20to%20friends%20and%20family%20to%20pitch%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20financial%20risks%20we%20could%20ever%20take%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marshall%20to%20CNBC.%20%26quot%3BWe%20really%20took%20quite%20a%20risk%20in%20pouring%20not%20only%20all%20of%20our%20money%20into%20it%20but%20also%20all%20of%20our%20time%20and%20energy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f6011bab-a226-4786-8cae-18fb32509450%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20their%20'it'%20factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECoffee%20shops%20are%20a%20dime%20a%20dozen%20these%20days%20%E2%80%94%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdailycoffeenews.com%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Fled-by-big-chains-us-coffee-shop-market-surpasses-40000-stores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20there%20are%20now%20more%20than%2040%2C000%20in%20the%20US.%20But%20Maman%20and%20its%20owners%20have%20made%20it%20a%20standout%20by%20honing%20in%20on%20a%20few%20distinct%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInspiration%20for%20Maman%20%E2%80%94%20the%20French%20word%20for%20%26quot%3Bmother%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20menu%20was%20born%20from%20the%20foods%20they%20ate%20as%20kids.%20Sormonte%20grew%20up%20in%20Southern%20France%20and%20Marshall%20in%20Toronto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarshall%20told%20CNBC%20that%20they%20chose%20the%20name%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Bthe%20feeling%20of%20warmth%20and%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20asked%20ourselves%2C%20'Who%20is%20your%20favorite%20chef%3F'%20We%20both%20said%20%26quot%3BMaman%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20we%20both%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20kitchen%20with%20our%20mom%2C%26quot%3B%20Sormonte%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aesthetic%20inside%20its%20locations%20matches%2C%20with%20its%20blue%20and%20white%20china%2C%20country%20wood%20furniture%2C%20and%20floral%20touches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20coming%20here%20for%20the%20ambiance%20%5Band%5D%20for%20the%20vibe%2C%20for%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BGood%20food%20and%20coffee%20is%20easy%20to%20find%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20places.%20So%20you%20need%20that%20little%20something%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221723%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maman%20Nutty%20Chocolate%20Chip%20Cookie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e874f7e92e8ba2e3a511383%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22969%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20nutty%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%20from%20Maman.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22429951d0-42d0-4d88-96ba-d219fb9a0bdc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20standout%20menu%20item%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20had%20breakfast%20dishes%2C%20coffee%20drinks%2C%20and%20Instagram-worthy%20aesthetics%20down%2C%20one%20item%20in%20their%20pasty%20case%20put%20Maman%20on%20the%20map%20in%20its%20early%20days%3A%20their%20%26quot%3Bnutty%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20first%20month%20of%20being%20open%2C%20Maman%20was%20featured%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.grubstreet.com%2F2014%2F10%2Fmaman-chocolate-chip-cookie.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Magazine%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20said%20it%20had%20%26quot%3BNYC's%20most%20impressive%20new%20chocolate-chip%20cookie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attention%20catapulted%20them%20into%20the%20spotlight%20and%20spread%20the%20word%20fast%20about%20their%20existence.%20In%20its%20first%20year%2C%20Maman%20made%20about%20%242%20million%20in%20revenue%2C%20according%20to%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257c313ba-d581-4bd5-991a-f32e54a4ea7c%5C%22%3E%3Cs