eer-lawsuit-martha-ava-duvernay-when-they-see-us-1236042345%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fnetflix-baby-reindeer-lawsuit-martha-ava-duvernay-when-they-see-us-1236042345%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TikTok%20To%20Be%20Bought%20By%20US%20Billionaire%3F%20What%20He%20Says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrank%20McCourt%2C%20a%20US%20real%20estate%20billionaire%2C%20aims%20to%20buy%20TikTok%20to%20rescue%20the%20internet%20from%20the%20clutches%20of%20major%20platforms%20that%20he%20firmly%20believes%20are%20destroying%20society%20and%20endangering%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20United%20States%2C%20McCourt%20is%20best%20known%20as%20the%20former%20owner%20of%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Dodgers%20baseball%20team%2C%20while%20in%20Europe%20he%20is%20the%20current%20proprietor%20of%20storied%20football%20club%20Olympique%20de%20Marseille%20that%20counts%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20among%20its%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20McCourt%20has%20railed%20against%20the%20power%20of%20the%20big%20tech%20platforms%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20harming%20children%20and%20helping%20send%20the%20world%20off%20the%20rails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20being%20manipulated%20by%20these%20big%20platforms.%20And%20that's%20why%20we%20see%20in%20free%20societies%20everywhere%2C%20there's%20sort%20of%20the%20world%20on%20fire%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20McCourt%20told%20AFP%20at%20the%20Collision%20tech%20conference%20in%20Toronto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20political%20upheaval%20in%20France%2C%20where%20the%20far-right%20could%20secure%20a%20decisive%20victory%20in%20the%20upcoming%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20as%20the%20latest%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20agitation%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20chaos%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20polarization.%20Well%2C%20you%20know%20what%2C%20the%20algorithms%20are%20working%20well.%20They're%20keeping%20us%20in%20that%20constant%20state.%20It's%20time%20for%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcCourt%20said%20he%20was%20initially%20motivated%20to%20act%20by%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20social%20media%20to%20his%20own%20seven%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20internet%20is%20predatory.%20It's%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20damage%20to%20kids.%20We%20see%20the%20anxiety%2C%20the%20depression%2C%20and%20an%20epidemic%20now%20of%20children%20taking%20their%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20problem%2C%20McCourt%20is%20campaigning%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20internet%26quot%3B%20which%2C%20he%20claims%2C%20would%20wrest%20control%20of%20the%20web%20away%20from%20major%20platforms%20like%20Instagram%2C%20YouTube%2C%20TikTok%2C%20or%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20platforms%20have%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20individual%20attributes%20about%20each%20of%20us.%20And%20it's%20not%20just%20where%20we%20shop%20or%20what%20we%20like%20to%20eat%20or%20where%20we%20physically%20are%20present.%20It's%20about%20how%20we%20think%2C%20how%20we%20emote%2C%20how%20we%20react%2C%20how%20we%20behave%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcCourt%20envisions%20a%20new%20internet%20that%20he%20describes%20as%20an%20open-source%2C%20decentralized%20protocol%20where%20users%20control%20their%20own%20data%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20social%20media%20app%20they%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcquiring%20TikTok%20would%20give%20his%20project%20known%20as%20Project%20Liberty%20a%20whole%20new%20scale%2C%20bringing%20in%20its%20legions%20of%20users%2C%20mostly%20younger%20people%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProject%20Liberty%20counts%20internet%20pioneer%20Tim%20Berners-Lee%20as%20a%20supporter%2C%20along%20with%20Jonathan%20Haidt%2C%20an%20NYU%20professor%20whose%20latest%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Anxious%20Generation%2C%26quot%3B%20argues%20that%20the%20effects%20of%20social%20media%20on%20young%20people%20have%20been%20devastating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Undemocratic'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcCourt%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20eyeing%20the%20Chinese-owned%20platform%2C%20with%20Trump's%20former%20secretary%20of%20the%20treasury%2C%20Steve%20Mnuchin%2C%20also%20advancing%20a%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20plans%2C%20which%20some%20say%20are%20far-fetched%2C%20follow%20a%20bill%20signed%20by%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20in%20April%20that%20gives%20TikTok%20270%20days%20to%20find%20a%20non-Chinese%20buyer%20or%20face%20a%20ban%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20hardly%20a%20sure%20thing%20that%20TikTok%20will%20end%20up%20being%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20fighting%20the%20law%20in%20US%20courts%2C%20and%20the%20Chinese%20government%20has%20said%20it%20would%20not%20accept%20the%20divestment%20of%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20most%20successful%20tech%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20government's%20concern%20is%20that%20the%20data%20of%20170%20million%20Americans%20is%20being%20scraped%20and%20sent%20to%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20%26quot%3Bof%20course%26quot%3B%20poses%20a%20national%20security%20threat%2C%20McCourt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20that%20this%20TikTok%20issue%20will%20make%20that%20light%20bulb%20go%20off%20for%20people%2C%20and%20they'll%20realize%20(that%20even%20on%20other%20platforms)%20their%20data%20is%20being%20scraped%20and%20shipped%20somewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20China%2C%20but%20it's%20going%20somewhere%20controlled%20by%20someone%20who%20has%20everything%20about%20you%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20correct.%20That's%20undemocratic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3