hing%20different%20here%20(in%20Barbados).%20Yuzi%20(Chahal)%20or%20Kuldeep%20(Yadav)%20could%20be%20used%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dravid%2C%20while%20interacting%20with%20the%20media%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20Super%20Eight%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20lucky%20to%20have%20players%20with%20all-round%20abilities.%20We%20had%20eight%20batters%20but%20we%20(also)%20had%20seven%20bowling%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravid%20also%20added%20that%20India%20will%20be%20flexible%20with%20its%20batting%20order%20and%20change%20it%20as%20per%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20situation%20is%20unique.%20Can't%20set%20it%20in%20stone.%20I%20believe%20in%20flexibility.%20The%20Pakistan%20game%20we%20moved%20Axar%20(Patel)%2C%20specifically%20thinking%20around%20it...%20Rishabh%20(Pant)%20up%20the%20order%20(at%20No.%203)%2C%20lots%20of%20thinking%20goes%20into%20it.%20I%20don't%20think%20in%20Tests%20(cricket)%2C%20we%20will%20have%20that%20flexibility.%20In%20T20s%20where%20it%20is%20a%20lot%20about%20match-ups%2C%20you%20see%20it%20happening%20more%20(flexibility%20in%20batting%20position).%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatch-up%20in%20cricketing%20lingo%20means%20when%20a%20bowler%20or%20a%20batter%20holds%20sway%20over%20a%20particular%20player%20in%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20crucial%20moment%20when%20India%20were%20struggling%20at%2019%2F2%20with%20both%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20Axar%20was%20promoted%20at%20No.%204%20and%20he%20made%20a%20useful%2020%20off%2018%20balls%20against%20arch-rivals%20Pakistan%20in%20