%20has%20been%20increased%20by%20Rs%20117%2C%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20said%20at%20a%20Cabinet%20briefing%20on%20Wednesday.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20legal%20guarantee%20for%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20has%20been%20a%20long-standing%20demand%20of%20farmers%20who%20have%20staged%20large-scale%20protests%2C%20including%20some%20held%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20to%20press%20for%20it.%20The%20MSP%20decision%20is%20also%20significant%20because%20it%20comes%20ahead%20of%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20states%20like%20Haryana%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand%2C%20which%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20later%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20always%20given%20preference%20to%20farmers.%20The%20first%20decision%20in%20the%20third%20term%20was%20taken%20for%20farmers.%20In%20today's%20Cabinet%20meeting%20also%2C%20a%20very%20important%20decision%20was%20taken%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20farmers.%20The%20Kharif%20season%20is%20beginning%20and%20the%20Cabinet%20has%20approved%20a%20minimum%20support%20price%20of%2014%20crops%20for%20the%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%202018%20Union%20Budget%2C%20the%20government%20of%20India%20had%20taken%20a%20clear%20policy%20decision%20that%20the%20MSP%20has%20to%20be%20at%20least%201.5%20times%20the%20cost%20of%20production.%20Today's%20decision%20is%20in%20line%20with%20this%20principle.%20The%20cost%20has%20been%20established%20in%20a%20scientific%20manner%20and%20is%20based%20on%20a%20study%20by%20the%20Commission%20for%20Agricultural%20Costs%20and%20Prices%20in%20various%20districts%20and%20tehsils%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MSP%20for%20paddy%20for%20the%20season%20has%20been%20increased%20by%205.35%25%2C%20or%20Rs%20117%2C%20to%20Rs%202%2C300%20per%20quintal%20and%2C%20as%20a%20comparison%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20the%20price%20was%201%2C310%20in%202013-14.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minimum%20support%20of%20cotton%20has%20also%20been%20increased%20to%207%2C121%20for%20the%20normal%20variety%20and%207%2C521%20for%20another%20variety%2C%20which%20is%20Rs%20510%20higher%20than%20the%20previous%20MSP.%20Millets%20have%20been%20a%20focus%20area%20for%20PM%20Modi%20and%2C%20among%20them%2C%20the%20MSP%20for%20jowar%20has%20been%20set%20at%20Rs%203%2C371%2C%20for%20ragi%20it%20is%20Rs%204%2C290%2C%20for%20bajra%20it%20is%202%2C625%20and%20maize%20is%20at%20Rs%202%2C225.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20pulses%2C%20the%20MSP%20for%20moong%20has%20been%20decided%20at%20Rs%208%2C682%2C%20tur%20at%20Rs%207%2C550%20-%20Rs%20550%20higher%20than%20the%20previous%20figure%20-%20and%20Rs%207%2C400%20for%20urad.%20The%20MSP%20for%20oilseeds%2C%20like%20sunflower%20and%20groundnut%2C%20has%20also%20seen%20an%20increase%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20the%20increased%20MSP%20will%20mean%20a%20gain%20of%20Rs%2035%2C000%20crore%20to%20farmers%20over%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20released%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20as%20part%20of%20the%2017th%20instalment%20of%20the%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%2C%20an%20income%20support%20scheme%20under%20which%20farmers%20get%20up%20to%20Rs%206%2C000%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20Varanasi%20after%20being%20elected%20the%20MP%20from%20there%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%20he%20had%20also%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BAgriculture%20will%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20making%20India%20the%20third-largest%20economy.%20We%20have%20to%20think%20global%20and%20become%20a%20leader%20in%20exports.%20Varanasi's%20Langda%20mango%2C%20Jaunpur's%20radish%20and%20Ghazipur's%20ladyfinger%20are%20now%20reaching%20foreign%20markets...%20We%20have%20to%20take%20the%20country%20to%20new%20heights%20in%20packaged%20food%20exports.%20My%20dream%20is%20to%20see%20an%20Indian%20food%20product%20on%20every%20dining%20table%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20Decisions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Cabinet%20has%20also%20approved%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20major%20greenfield%20port%20at%20Vadhavan%20near%20Dahanu%20in%20Maharastra.%20The%20Project%20will%20be%20constructed%20by%20the%20Vadhavan%20Port%20Project%20Limited%2C%20a%20special%20purpose%20vehicle%20(SPV)%20formed%20by%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Port%20Authority%20and%20Maharashtra%20Maritime%20Board%20with%20a%20shareholding%20of%2074%25%20and%2026%25%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20viability%20gap%20funding%20(VGF)%20scheme%20for%20offshore%20wind%20energy%20projects%20at%20a%20total%20outlay%20of%20Rs%207%2C453%20crore%20has%20also%20been%20greenlit.%20This%20includes%20Rs%206%2C853%20crore%20for%20the%20installation%20and%20commissioning%20of%201%20gigawatt%20(GW)%20of%20offshore%20wind%20energy%20projects%20-%20500%20MW%20each%20off%20the%20coasts%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20proposal%20by%20the%20Airports%20Authority%20of%20India%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20International%20Airport%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20including%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20new%20terminal%20building%20and%20runway%20extension%2C%20has%20also%20been%20approved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718812140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fl8gvf28_wheat-generic-wheat-arrival-in-punjab-amritsar-ani_625x300_28_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-approves-minimum-support-price-msp-for-14-crops-says-it-is-at-least-1-5-times-the-cost-of-production-5924902%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20major%20decision%2C%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20has%20approved%20a%20minimum%20support%20price%20of%20at%20least%20cost%20plus%2050%25%20for%2014%20crops%20ahead%20of%20the%20Kharif%20sowing%20season.%20The%20minimum%20support%20price%20of%20paddy%20has%20been%20increased%20by%20Rs%20117.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-approves-minimum-support-price-msp-for-14-crops-says-it-is-at-least-1-5-times-the-cost-of-production-5924902%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-approves-minimum-support-price-msp-for-14-crops-says-it-is-at-least-1-5-times-the-cost-of-production-5924902%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-approves-minimum-support-price-msp-for-14-crops-says-it-is-at-least-1-5-times-the-cost-of-production-5924902%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trend%20upshift%20in%20growth%20post%20pandemic%2C%20rises%20to%208%25%20in%202021-24%3A%20RBI%20report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718812123000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F29%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1716971500-7279.JPG%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Ftrend-upshift-in-growth-post-pandemic-rises-to-8-in-2021-24-rbi-report-124061901019_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Strong%20revival%20in%20pvt%20investment%20imp%20for%20growth%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Ftrend-upshift-in-growth-post-pandemic-rises-to-8-in-2021-24-rbi-report-124061901019_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Ftrend-upshift-in-growth-post-pandemic-rises-to-8-in-2021-24-rbi-report-124061901019_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Ftrend-upshift-in-growth-post-pandemic