%20Whenever%20anyone%20asked%20Poorvi%2C%20a%20nutritionist%20and%20naturopath%2C%20what%20she%20wanted%20for%20her%20big%20day%2C%20her%20answer%20remained%20the%20same%20over%20the%20years%3A%20a%20simple%2C%20eco-friendly%20wedding%20at%20her%20family%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20decided%20to%20marry%20her%20husband%2C%20an%20organic%20farmer%2C%20his%20family%20readily%20agreed%20to%20her%20non-negotiable%20requirement%20of%20a%20sustainable%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sugarcane%20mantapa%20doubled%20up%20as%20a%20meal%20for%20the%20cows!%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353338%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20sugarcane%20mantapa%20later%20doubled%20up%20as%20a%20meal%20for%20the%20cows!%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20sugarcane%20%3Cem%3Emantapa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(wedding%20pavilion)%20to%20decorations%20using%20mango%20and%20coconut%20leaves%20from%20the%20farm%2C%20to%20a%20handwash%20where%20the%20water%20was%20recycled%20into%20the%20farm%2C%20to%20steel%20cutlery%20and%20banana%20leaves%2C%20every%20aspect%20was%20meticulously%20planned.%20All%20the%20wet%20waste%20was%20composted%20in%20the%20farm%E2%80%99s%20vermicompost%20pit%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Emantapa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20chopped%20up%20and%20served%20as%20a%20delicious%20meal%20for%20cows!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20two-day%20event%2C%20the%20venue%20was%20spotlessly%20clean%2C%20with%20all%20waste%20returned%20to%20mother%20nature.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20family%20pulled%20it%20together%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGoing%20back%20to%20the%20basics%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Poorvi%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20was%20rooted%20in%20sustainability%2C%20where%20it%20was%20a%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20has%20been%20running%20this%20organic%20farm%20for%20over%2040%20years.%20Everything%20there%20is%20composted%20and%20these%20are%20general%20practices%20followed%20in%20villages.%20My%20parents%20follow%20these%20principles%20in%20their%20everyday%20life%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20Poorvi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-11-at-19.04.13-1-min-1718768381-500x881.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20decorations%20were%20all%20locally%20sourced%20and%20were%20later%20composted%20at%20the%20farm%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-11-at-19.04.13-1-min-1718768381-500x881.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-11-at-19.04.13-1-min-1718768381-170x300.jpeg%20170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-11-at-19.04.13-1-min-1718768381-768x13