n%20Shivamogga.%20It%20is%20also%20something%20that%20our%20cows%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Poorvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20shared%20her%20vision%20with%20the%20decorators%2C%20they%20came%20up%20with%20more%20ideas%20and%20were%20excited%20about%20not%20using%20plastic.%20They%20ensured%20that%20the%20aesthetics%20weren%E2%80%99t%20compromised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20and%20biggest%20step%20was%20catering%2C%20where%20most%20of%20the%20waste%20is%20generated%20during%20weddings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6d2_KetPkV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6d2_KetPkV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6d2_KetPkV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Dr.Poorvi%20Bhat%20%7C%20Nutrition%20%26amp%3B%20Wellness%20(%40herbeshwari)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Down%20to%20Earth%20report%20suggests%20that%2010%20to%2015%20percent%20of%20food%20is%20wasted%20at%20every%20wedding%2C%20with%20a%20minimum%20of%2050%20kg%20and%20up%20to%20800%20kg.%20During%20the%2023-day%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eshaadi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eseason%E2%80%99%20from%20November%20to%20December%202023%2C%20the%20country%20witnessed%20over%203.5%20million%20weddings.%20Imagine%20the%20amount%20of%20food%20wasted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20any%20waste%2C%20the%20family%20decided%20against%20using%20plastic%20bottles%20or%20paper%20cups.%20They%20rented%20steel%20cutlery%20and%20used%20an%20auto-clean%20machine%20to%20wash%20and%20sterilise%20it.%20They%20also%20served%20food%20on%20traditional%20banana%20leaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20opted%20for%20a%20local%20menu%20using%20freshly%20grown%20seasonal%20ingredients.%20We%20had%20the%20machine%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20cutlery%20was%20clean.%20We%20had%20big%20reusable%20water%20cans%20for%20drinking%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20bride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20washing%20hands%2C%20they%20placed%20drums%20of%20water%20with%20mugs%20in%20a%20strategic%20location%20where%20the%20water%20would%20directly%20go%20to%20the%20mango%20trees.%20They%20refrained%20from%20installing%20taps%20to%20prevent%20excess%20water%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20food%20wastage%2C%20they%20instructed%20the%20caterers%20to%20serve%20in%20small%20quantities%20and%20as%20per%20the%20guest%E2%80%99s%20wishes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20usually%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20serving%20large%20quantities%20of%20food%20which%20most%20people%20can%E2%80%99t%20eat.%20We%20wanted%20the%20guests%20to%20be%20happy%20and%20therefore%20served%20small%20portions%2C%20which%20could%20be%20refilled%20at%20will%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC7vpU43pyIL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20h