2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20log%20in%20design%20inputs%20about%20the%20infrastructure%20into%20our%20software%2C%20we%20create%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20for%20operating%20the%20plant%20in%20real-time.%20Our%20client%20can%20visualise%20the%20asset%20(wastewater%20treatment%20plant)%20and%20can%20gauge%20its%20analytics%20from%20how%20much%20wastewater%20is%20getting%20treated%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20treatment%20being%20achieved%20and%20whether%20the%20equipment%20is%20functioning%20properly%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mansi%20during%20an%20episode%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH3moOD09wNk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShark%20Tank%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20client%20has%20a%20complete%20online%20software%20before%20them%20to%20visualise%20their%20asset.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20problem%20inside%20the%20plant%2C%20our%20software%20can%20assess%20and%20interpret%20data%20using%20AI%20to%20detect%20it.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20that%20clients%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20to%20be%20on%20our%20software%20to%20manage%20these%20issues.%20Management%20actions%20are%20happening%20automatically%2C%20whether%20through%20equipment%20control%20or%20by%20telling%20operators%20directly%20what%20to%20do.%20Clients%20just%20receive%20alert%20notifications%20on%20their%20WhatsApp%20number%20to%20make%20things%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20product%20innovation%2C%20Mansi%20argues%2C%20also%20allows%20them%20to%20unlock%20business%20model%20innovation.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20becoming%20an%20add-on%20cost%20for%20facilities%20like%20our%20competitors%2C%20we%20can%20de-risk%20adoption%20and%20offer%20guaranteed%20savings%20through%20two%20models%20which%20no%20one%20else%20in%20the%20market%20can%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mansi%2C%20speaking%20to%20The