y%20through%20WhatsApp%20and%20live%20dashboards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20Finally%2C%20it%20%E2%80%98solves%E2%80%99%20the%20need%20by%20executing%20the%20required%20actions%20directly%20through%20automated%20workflows%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20training%20onsite%20teams%2C%20guiding%20their%20daily%20workflow%20and%20validating%20their%20work%20or%20managing%20the%20physical%20operation%20of%20equipment%20through%20our%20in-platform%20automation%20manager.%20When%20things%20start%20going%20wrong%2C%20it%20uses%20data%20streams%20from%20onsite%20sensors%20and%20electrical%20panels%20to%20diagnose%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20issue%20and%20drive%20issue%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20recommend%20operational%20and%20physical%20improvements.%20This%20approach%20has%20transformed%20defunct%20facilities%20while%20reducing%20their%20costs%20by%20up%20to%2066%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Here's%20how%20you%20can%20do%20water%20treatment%20with%20Digital%20Paani%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-150x79.jpg