erindia.com%2F351690%2Fyash-dayal-sharma-fertile-beeghas-organic-waste-vermicompost-stubble-burning-train-farmers-soil-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efarmers%20get%20fair%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well%20as%20security%20that%20their%20produce%20will%20be%20sold.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGram%20Unnati%20is%20working%20in%20eight%20states%20across%2018-20%20different%20commodities%20like%20cereals%2C%20oilseeds%2C%C2%A0%20pulses%2C%20spices%2C%20fresh%20fruits%20and%20vegetables.%20Their%20target%20is%20to%20reach%20a%20million%20farmers%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Gram%20Unnati%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718022791000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352547%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gurugram-based%20Aneesh%20Jain%20quit%20his%20consulting%20job%20to%20become%20a%20%E2%80%98consultant%E2%80%99%20for%20farmers.%20His%20startup%2C%20Gram%20Unnati%2C%20is%20an%20agricultural%20value%20chain%20services%20platform%20that%20bridges%20gaps%20between%20institutional%20buyers%20and%20marginal%20farmers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Are%20the%20Spices%20in%20Your%20Kitchen%20Adulterated%3F%205%20Easy%20Home%20Tests%20To%20Find%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20essence%20of%20any%20Indian%20meal%20lies%20in%20its%20spices.%20However%2C%20many%20spices%20that%20we%20buy%20from%20the%20market%20can%20contain%20impurities.%20Manufacturers%20often%20add%20colouring%2C%20flour%2C%20and%20even%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F234603%2Fharmful-chemicals-laundry-detergent-you-should-avoid-the-better-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20harmful%20chemicals%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20enhance%20the