marks%20in%20the%20second%20attempt.%20So%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20attempt%2084%20questions%20in%20my%20third%20attempt%2C%20which%20helped%20me%20score%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Prepare%20short%20notes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20changes%20that%20he%20made%20in%20his%20strategy%20on%20the%20third%20attempt%2C%20Aaditya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20prepared%20notes%20for%20most%20of%20the%20subjects.%20Although%20note-making%20was%20additional%20work%2C%20it%20helped%20me%20understand%20concepts%20better.%20It%20helps%20to%20save%20time%20instead%20of%20checking%20source%20material%20repeatedly.%20It%20also%20helps%20for%20effective%20revision.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20two%20failed%20attempts%2C%20Aaditya%20cleared%20UPSC%20CSE%20in%202022%20with%20an%20impressive%20AIR%20of%2048.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352537%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20two%20failed%20attempts%2C%20Aaditya%20cleared%20UPSC%20CSE%20in%202022%20with%20an%20impressive%20AIR%20of%2048.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20did%20not%20pressurise%20myself%20much.%20If%20I%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20study%2C%20I%20would%20sit%20in%20a%20corner%20with%20my%20coffee%20mug%2C%20close%20my%20eyes%2C%20and%20recall%20my%20notes.%20If%20I%20missed%20some%20point%2C%20then%20I%20would%20immediately%20refer%20to%20my%20notes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20suggests%20aspirants%20make%20notes%20only%20after%20first%20reading.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20make%20notes%20majorly%20for%20Acts%20and%20rules.%20You%20can%20make%20notes%20by%20summarising%20the%20topic.%20Make%20sure%20that%20you%20do%20not%20end%20up%20writing%20another%20book.%20Final%20notes%20should%20be%2033%20percent%20of%20all%20topics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Know%20your%20DAF%20well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20says%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fupsc-cse-how-to-fill-detailed-application-form-daf-ias-irs-ifs-officers-share-tips-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDetailed%20Application%20Form%20%3C%2Fa%3E(DAF)%20is%20very%20crucial%20for%20the%20personality%20test%20round.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20Mains%2C%20candidates%20need%20to%20fill%20out%20DAF%20which%20contains%20details%20like%20hometown%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20hobbies%2C%20and%20interests.%20Do%20not%20fill%20them%20recklessly%20as%20initial%20questions%20can%20be%20framed%20from%20DAF%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInterviews%20are%20very%20subjective.%20The%20first%20question%20asked%20in%20the%20interview%20determines%20the%20interview%20flow%20and%20whether%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20mould%20it%20in%20your%20favour.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20command%20of%20your%20DAF%2C%20then%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20sail%20through%20the%20interview%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20DAF%2C%20Aaditya%20mentioned%20listening%20to%20Ramcharitmanas%20(an%20epic%20poem%20that%20contains%20the%20deeds%20of%20Lord%20Rama)%20and%20watching%20Korean%20dramas%20as%20his%20interests.%20This%20framed%20his%20interview%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20similarities%20and%20differences%20between%20ancient%20values%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Indian%20and%20Korean%20societies.%20Another%20question%20was%20based%20on%20the%20division%20of%20Korea%20and%20its%20war%20history.%20Later%20on%2C%20we%20spoke%20on%20the%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20which%20I%20did%20not%20mention%20in%20my%20DAF%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aaditya%20secured%20190%20marks%20in%20the%20UPSC%20interview%20round.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352529%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAaditya%20secured%20190%20marks%20in%20the%20UPSC%20interview%20round.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20interviewer%20was%20a%20war%20veteran%20himself.%20So%2C%20you%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20interviewer%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Be%20yourself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20people%20warned%20Aaditya%20for%20his%20blunt%20and%20outrageous%20attitude.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20said%20it%20would%20cost%20me%20final%20marks%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20tone%20down%20my%20personality.%20Only%20a%20few%20mentors%20supported%20me.%20There%20is%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about%20if%20you%20express%20yourself%20properly%20and%20your%20views%20are%20backed%20with%20logic%2C%20moral%2C%20ethical%2C%20and%20legal%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20believes%20aspirants%20must%20seek%20one-on-one%20interviews%20with%20a%20known%20person%20who%20can%20really%20assess%20their%20personality%20and%20attitude%20in%20order%20to%20help%20build%20confidence%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F281037%2Fhow-to-crack-upsc-interview-tips-ias-officer-twitter-personality-test%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Find%20your%20salvation%20in%20chaos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20kept%20Aaditya%20motivated%20throughout%20his%20preparation%20journey%20and%20two%20failed%20attempts%20was%20his%20ability%20to%20calm%20himself.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20doubted%20myself%20or%20felt%20frustrated%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20turn%20to%20listening%20to%20Ramcharitmanas%2C%20which%20was%20a%20pillar%20of%20self-motivation%20for%20me.%20Similarly%2C%20aspirants%20can%20find%20their%20own%20ways%20of%20keeping%20calm%20with%20music%20or%20meditation%20as%20such%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20IAS%20Aaditya%20Pandey.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718019485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebet